{"tid":211421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[一件趣事] 搭地鐵俾個廢老踢腳，迫我讓座","createTime":"2017-04-21T15:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T11:54:38.000Z","uid":28938,"like":689,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ac28a3588a00ab40f37947286c77efdc29b5e495","tid":211421,"uid":28938,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:26:00.000Z","msg":"時間：約晚上9時半<br />\n路線：觀塘線<br />\n<br />\n我無坐關愛座，聽住歌低頭打機，無啦啦有隻腳踢落我。<br />\n<br />\n我抬頭一望，係個廢老黎，就啤住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n廢老：喂後生仔讓個位黎坐下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我：你講還講駛唔駛踢我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廢老：叫左你幾聲啦，扮聽唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我：我聽緊歌呀，點聽到你講野呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廢老：唔好講咁多，同我行開。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我：我原本都會讓俾你，但依家你踢我，我唔讓，你吹咩？你再踢我報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廢老無言以對，走左去第二卡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f044086d0291379ae80afd1a51cc9757c8d2d7","tid":211421,"uid":9851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:28:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正皮"},{"pid":"42bb1dc2de48462f9c255b36f893244f68046ee5","tid":211421,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:28:49.000Z","msg":"報警撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0a60edabdf4aaeadbdc4254dedb9f70f94683d","tid":211421,"uid":41944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:28:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ngood job"},{"pid":"359